BBEX3.A.TMT.EUR.CA.AC.A04: Exchange rates for the euro in Turkmenistan / EUR 1 = TMT ... (middle)
General: Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1; for exchange rates until 2008, see BBEX3:A:TMM:EUR:CA:AC:A04.
Source: Central Bank of Turkmenistan, Ashgabat.
Methodology: Calculated on the basis of mid-month and month-end rates.
Comment on 2009: Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1.
